```{r gallbladder 31815746, include=FALSE}

PMID_31815746 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('31815746', database = 'PubMed')

citation_31815746 <- paste0(PMID_31815746$journal,' ', PMID_31815746$year, ' ', PMID_31815746$month,';', PMID_31815746$volume,'(', PMID_31815746$number,'):', PMID_31815746$pages)

PubMed_31815746 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_31815746$eprint)

doi_31815746 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_31815746$doi)

Sys.sleep(2)
```
